@node Main "Colorit - Documentation"

                             'Colorit' 1.21

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Colorit' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} in which there are two square boards
filled with coloured tiles. The board at left has a pattern and the other
is randomly shuffled. The @{" goal " link play} of the game is to move the tiles of
the shuffled board until it matches the other board in the least amount
of moves possible.

  Have fun!

