@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Colorit" where you want
on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or
Libraries are needed. The only requirement is that your Workbench must
have at least 8 colours.

                             How to play?

  To play, just click on a tile in the board at right, that tile must
always be surrounded by 8 other tiles. Each time a tile is clicked on,
the 8 surrounding tiles will 'rotate' clockwise by one position. Continue
to move the tiles, until the board matches the board on the left. Try
to complete the game with the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

OPTIONS

  -@{b}New Game@{ub}:               Restarts the game (or Left Amiga + "N").

  -@{b}Mini Board...Big Board@{ub}: Selects between the 4x4, 6x6, 8x8 or 10x10
                           size of game board.

